p_jp_player_position.action:
var panValue = args[0] > 0 ? Math.min(args[0], 0.75) : Math.max(args[0], -0.75);
me.bu_jetpack.effects[0].pan = panValue;

p_music_samples_game_over.action:
Util.hurry_up = false; me.sq_sequencer1.syncPattern({beat:4, duration:0.1},me.pt_fallback_GameOver); me.sq_sequencer1.stopAll({beat:4},me.pt_fallback_GameOver);
me.sq_sequencer1.syncPattern({beat:8, absolute: 4, duration:0.1},me.pt_fallback_Lounge);

p_music_ultralounge.action: Util.hurry_up = false;me.sq_sequencer1.stopAll({beat:4},me.pt_ultralounge, me.pt_ultraloungetransition);  if (Util.ultraloungestarted) {me.sq_sequencer1.syncPattern({beat:8},me.pt_ultralounge); me.sq_sequencer1.syncPattern({beat:4},me.pt_ultraloungetransition);} else {me.sq_sequencer1.syncPattern({beat:4},me.pt_ultralounge);}; Util.ultraloungestarted = true;

p_pd_sled_position.action:
var panValue = args[0] > 0 ? Math.min(args[0], 0.5) : Math.max(args[0], -0.5);
me.bu_pd_slide.effects[0].pan = panValue;
